entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: The illegal research laboratory has been destroyed and Coronet City is safe from rampaging engineered creatures. Great work!
entries.journal_entry_description: Destroy their research by overloading their central computer.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: All research in this lab needs to be destroyed.  Damage the central computer and with any luck, it will wipe out all traces of research.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Lt. Joth and tell him about your success!
